query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `rag_search_history` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `query` text NOT NULL,
  `queryEmbedding` text,
  `resultCount` int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `topChunkIds` json,
  `conversationId` int,
  `searchDurationMs` int,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `rag_search_history_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`),
  INDEX `rag_search_history_user_id_idx` (`userId`),
  INDEX `rag_search_history_created_at_idx` (`createdAt`)
);
